Benchmark Prediction & Evaluation Results
We retrain and evaluate 40 state-of-the-art (SOTA) methods in the field of salient object detection (SOD) and underwater salient object detection (USOD) for comprehensive benchmark comparison.
1. Predicted Saliency Maps (USOD10K)
Baidu Netdisk: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1EpnE07lgamyaUIUZWdccqAFetch Code: usod
Google Drive: https://drive.google.com/file/1D4wLLol84DEpolmO-cYpo2jaiBY7Ufn
